Finally got under 40! After a poor start I got a good Resort. Ridge and Temple we quite average. But the Reflection with only a single quick death was really awesome, I got a PB there by more than 40s! The summit was also better than average (except the beginning when I was too excited due to the Reflection), so it was enough to reach this milestone.

This is my last run as my goal was reached. I wish a good luck to everyone here for keeping this great game alive!
